title: Motor Trend FlexTough Performance All Weather Rubber Car Floor Mats with Cargo Liner - Full Set Front & Rear Floor Mats for Cars Truck SUV, Automotive Floor Mats (Black)
description: Motor Trend mats are manufactured with the highest quality and safest material. Environmentally friendly means you and your family don't need to worry about toxins and odors that other rubber mats emit. These Motor Trend licensed products give your floor All-Weather protection and keeps your car free from any messes from spills, loose dirt, or water. These mats are made of EVA, the same safe materials as baby pacifiers, which means they are safe, environmentally friendly, and odor-less. You no longer have to worry about the strong rubber odors which make you dizzy and uncomfortable. Rated as non-toxic, safe and environmentally friendly by CGS labs. These rubber mats are easily trimmable to accommodate pedal placement and any necessary customization. Superior quality - minimal maintenance - ecofriendly. Extra-high ridgeline design with anti-slip nibbed backing.
